DYNAMIC RECON OPS — REWRITE
License & Attribution Notice
================================

ATTRIBUTION
-----------
This project is a community modification ("Rewrite") of DYNAMIC RECON OPS,
originally created by mbrdmn. All original mission design, concept, and code
credit belongs to the original author. This rewrite adds ACE3 integration, a
CBA-based scheduling rewrite, a lobby-parameter override system, additional
insertion types, combined-arms balancing, LAMBS Danger soft-compatibility, and
various fixes.

